First Department,

October, 1945.

(October 5, 1945.) Regal Garment Corporation et al., Respondents, v. Intercounty Properties Corp., Appellant.

Order unanimously affirmed, with $20 costs and disbursements. No opinion. Present — Martin, P. J., Townley, Glennon, Dore and Cohn, JJ.; Cohn, J., taking no part. [See post, p. 979.]
